  "response": "Inteliquent, a telecommunications company, typically recruits new graduates from a variety of universities, particularly those with strong engineering, computer science, and business programs. While I don't have access to real-time recruitment data or specific university lists for Inteliquent, companies in this industry often target institutions known for their programs in:\n\n- Computer Science\n- Computer Engineering\n- Electrical Engineering\n- Information Technology\n- Telecommunications\n- Business Administration (particularly with a focus on operations or technology)\n\nFor the most accurate information, it would be best to check Inteliquent's careers page or reach out to their HR department for details about campus recruitment and preferred majors. Additionally, platforms like LinkedIn can provide insights into where current employees graduated from.",
